    <item>
      <title>ChatGPT - GPT-5 Instant</title>
      <link>https://help.openai.com/en/articles/6825453-chatgpt-release-notes</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=openai.com&amp;sz=64&quot; alt=&quot;ChatGPT&quot; width=&quot;24&quot; height=&quot;24&quot; style=&quot;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:8px;&quot;/&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ChatGPT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The model is trained to more accurately detect and respond to potential signs of mental and emotional distress. These updates were guided by mental health experts, and help ChatGPT de-escalate conversations and point people to real-world crisis resources when appropriate, while still using language...&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://help.openai.com/en/articles/6825453-chatgpt-release-notes&quot;&gt;Read more →&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
